But you saw Kay&#39;s post, so now you have the right part #.  42-223

http://www.radioshack.com/product/index.jsp?productId=2944877&cp

And yes, you can get them for a little less on eBay ($1.65 + 2.50 s&h).  Some are mono, 
some are stereo.  This one from Radio Shack is stereo.  So, if you use eBay, pay attention to 
the description, and look for two black rings on the tip of the cable (rather than one, 
which is mono.)

Margaret

